p.d: Crystal Greenvelle lounges around at the villa with her two new tough guy friends - Vinney Star and Zack. They soon realize that she's in the mood for a little more than some fun in the sun, and follow her indoors to take the party to the next level. The clothes fall off, and these two get to teamwork on Crystal's fine booty. Watch as she gets twice the usual serving of cream pie from these two tattooed beasts.
